{"tid":462519,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)活死人地帶 活死人凶間","createTime":"2017-11-08T15:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T17:20:07.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5f41002f9b1c04a32a2780f4023d03fc580a7812","tid":462519,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T15:34:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=5UON4L6UOBkscdFMMj0xw1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=d3b82b2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=5UON4L6UOBkscdFMMj0xw1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=458766b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a6/Dawn_Of_The_Dead.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa6%2FDawn_Of_The_Dead.jpg&h=df38f70c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://5.blog.xuite.net/5/8/2/f/12092670/blog_141852/txt/9049154/8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5.blog.xuite.net%2F5%2F8%2F2%2Ff%2F12092670%2Fblog_141852%2Ftxt%2F9049154%2F8.jpg&h=e3c7a38d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一名居住在美國威斯康辛州密爾瓦基（Milwaukee）名叫安娜（Ana）的護士，在一如往常回到家休息。但隔天她的生活完全變了，丈夫變成了喪屍。好不容易開車逃離住宅，才知道整座城市已經陷入混亂，但突然有人要搶奪安娜的汽車，而撞上了一棵樹，安娜就暫時昏迷。（此時片頭音樂&quot;The Man Comes Around&quot;播放中，音樂還夾雜著各地因喪屍而陷入混亂的畫面）<br />\n<br />\n2.人類創造的文明世界已成為遙遠的記憶，現在的世界是一個無止無盡的噩夢，活人不斷受到活屍的攻擊，被它們生吞活剝，於是碩果僅存的人類為了活下去，只能躲在圍牆高築、防衛嚴密的城市堡壘，竭力抵抗活屍的攻擊。<br />\n少數有錢有勢的特權份子住在市內的綠洲高級大樓社區，在可怕活屍的威脅之下，試圖製造日子照舊的假象，維持著夜夜笙歌的糜爛生活。但是在大樓以外的城市街頭，平民百姓卻過著苦不堪言的生活，他們每天活在死亡的陰影之下，只能藉由賭博和嗑藥來麻醉自己，逃避這種地獄般的生活..<br />\n<br />\n11 35PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=5UON4L6UOBkscdFMMj0xw1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=36696620\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=5UON4L6UOBkscdFMMj0xw1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=80501c9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d0004ccb3cad1916d037aa1ccd812a121346a3","tid":462519,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74af99e63d5b450aaedc081079eb76f8d9d15c3d","tid":462519,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T16:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a3318d9962e2887c40baa424667fc1e450c55a","tid":462519,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T17:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}